Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My life, led lacking all splendor,\Nis heading toward a climax.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hanuki-san is a woman with no\Nfaults on an emotional or visual level,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but tonight she was just too... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry me away, before that person comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaori-san is a silent, lovely maiden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, we are fated to be apart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we are not able to meet, then I cannot\Ncontinue this relationship any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiko-san is classy and ladylike,\Nbut I can't see her like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:01:00.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tatami Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I was a brand-spanking\Nnew freshman university student{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and before me were held out circles' fliers far...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}surpassing my own\N information intake potential.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And through each of them I could see\Na gateway to that rose-colored campus life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Show Association
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A four year moratorium. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps it would be good to grant\Nchildren's aggressive dreams once in a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And perhaps a raven-haired maiden that\Nunderstands young boys' dreams may appear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've turned over a new leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Mochiguman...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never defeating anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never hurting anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you know it, trouble's quieted down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And has a big heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great, big, sincere heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, save Mochiguman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bad guys are trying\Nto kidnap the girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, make them change their ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change your ways! Change\Nyour ways! Change your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change your ways! Change your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, they ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Mochiguman intervened yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mochiguman for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got knocked around pretty good there...\NAnd it's only 3000 yen a performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I want to scout you. Big money guaranteed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Order what you'd like at the engineering\Ncafeteria and wait tomorrow at noon."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sounds pretty fishy to me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I spend my days in the Shimogamo Yuusuisou\Nboarding house behind Eizan Demachiyanagi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a three-story wooden building that\Nlooks like it could collapse at any time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so run-down that just\Nlooking at it is worrisome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps it'll be an important\Ncultural landmark soon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it's not difficult for me to imagine that\Nno one would mind if it just vanished one day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear viewers, be not surprised. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have been exchanging letters with\Na girl after some strange happenings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The most crucial things about exchanging\Nletters are that they be handwritten{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that you ne'er meet\Nyour partner in correspondence,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even should the very\Ncauldron of hell be unleashed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For far too oft that the elegant, precious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}relationship you had\Nfostered vanishes in an instant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her name is Higuchi Keiko-san, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I can tell her intelligence and\N education from her letters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She is surely my ideal woman. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You speak of this to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to keep it top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I want you to be a\Ncertain woman's bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a dangerous job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to protect her while I am gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been some... trouble lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a great number of\Npeople who would try to deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you, my friend, I can\Nrely on without reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as safe a bet as they come, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're a late\Nbloomer that is exceedingly shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore I have no need to worry\Nabout you doing anything... funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori is a very elegant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be very courteous to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do not wish the world at\Nlarge to learn of our private matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you speak about this\Nto others, then, for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His name was Jougasaki, and he was\Nthe president of the movie circle Misogi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He handed me Kaori's entertainment manual.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Things like no direct\Ncontact, her favorite drinks,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}not to run out of sweets, show her\Nmovies to make sure she doesn't get bored...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the essential principles\N were written down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:07:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go getting any weird thoughts, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't think of her as a doll at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her hair was carefully combed,\Nand her clothes were neat and elegant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her makeup, and fingernails,\Nand skin were all lovely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where did that elegant expression come from?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be nice if\NMr. Jougasaki came home soon, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Jougasaki is really a very\Nsimple and good person, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can't understand\Nhow Mr. Jougasaki feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I do think I'd\Nprefer a flesh and blood woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so the days where I would receive{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}payment for guarding while\NMr. Jougasaki was out continued.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Mr. Jougasaki came back,\NI would be quickly thrown out of the room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those days... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you've been moving up in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}'s bodyguard, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not underestimate\Nmy information-gathering network.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki-{\i1}san {\i0}may act that way,\Nbut he's really pure-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a very refined kind of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a far cry from some "dutch wife."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very high-quality\Nproduct called a "love doll."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that it's designed to be\Nloved and held dear by its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boor like you who thinks of it as nothing more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than a tool to satisfy one's\Nsexual desire wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then stay silent for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll have to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't chat, I'll be so lonely I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, I won't die as\Nlong as I'm making some idle chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no empathy for a soulless being like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be a bit more honest with yourself, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Jougasaki seemed to be\Nbusy at the moment shooting a film.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a modern remake of Alexander the Great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}which was supposed to be the\Nculmination of his work or something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Within his circle he was\Nvery popular and charismatic,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but his favorite was, of course, Kaori-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Around this time Mr. Jougasaki\Nwould be out of his room continuously,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and feeling sorry for the girl,\NI took tender care of her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although, of course, she was just a doll.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am exchanging letters with\Na real flesh and blood woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She always answers me back. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how beautiful Kaori-san\Nlooks to the eye, she will never respond.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The exquisite workmanship, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the delicate and lovely\Nworld Jougasaki had set up,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}made me think of her as\Na real person, occasionally.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ news is going great, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hanuki-san is a dental hygienist and an...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}older member of the\N English Conversation circle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It became a habit of ours to go\Nout to a café after each session.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it seemed like she only drank\Nalcohol with people she knew well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I had not yet been asked out for drinks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was wavering between\Nthe perverted dentist, Kubouzuka,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who continuously asked her out,\Nand a boyfriend that neglected her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally received a letter from my pen-pal\NKeiko-san saying she wanted to meet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I suppose that's proof that my literary skills{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}at lighting a maiden's heart\Non fire were nothing to scoff at.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I was not able to meet her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why? Because the me within the letters was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ever so slightly embellished\N from the me in reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:16.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiming to become an international actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that's what I \Nenvision my ideal self to be,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it will take a bit of time\Nfor the current me to catch up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, your place stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my place isn't safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on to Kaori here\Nfor a little while, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, I'm sorry. I know this is a filthy\Nplace, but please endure it for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you the same hourly\Nrate as before, at 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I don't have the cash on hand, so\Nplease allow me to do a direct bank deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was how Kaori-san\Nand I began living together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And wait, wasn't Mr. Jougasaki\Nthinking a bit too little of me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be that as it may, I never even dreamed that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}such a sweet campus life\Nwould be visited upon me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In these past two years\NI'd spent living uneventfully,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had never experienced such a brilliant event.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This and that... And two of each, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I returned from class,\NKaori-san was waiting for me in my room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That alone made the days enjoyable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was as if an intellectual,\Nraven-haired maiden{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}whose dreams were filled with\Nnovels had borrowed a corner of my room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One of these days she will\Nno longer be here, will she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say love comes in all forms,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it is dangerous to become lost\Nin the maze of such an insular love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I became fearful that I could no longer\Nfind the exit, I pressed deeper in along the path.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am pleased to eat ramen for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wished to eat it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure whether it's\Nto your taste, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's quite beautiful, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, she's Jougasaki's girlfriend, so\Nplease keep it a secret that we came to eat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you ate ramen! I can smell it on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat in your room! Eat outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But well, I'm not getting any younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just been doing\Nwhat I felt like up till now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I finish this movie I'm\Nfilming, I'm thinking of settling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll graduate, get a job, and\Nthen live once again with Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to pick up Kaori soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally I received an ultimatum from Keiko-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't meet with her this time,\Nall communication will likely cease.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I was still not the\Nman able to see Keiko-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna go out for some drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a report I need to write today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Good luck on your report!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And finally I was asked out for drinks\Nby Hanuki-san as proof that we were close,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}yet I ended up going home. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because tonight was the night Mr.\NJougasaki was coming to pick up Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I aim to become some\NRenaissance man of the sexual arts,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must narrow it down to one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}, please wait a little while!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a matter of life and death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I cannot allow Hanuki-san to be ruined\Nby some perverted dentist's intentions!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, at the hotel's lounge I was\Nmet with an unexpected turn of events.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For there in front of me was Mr. Jougasaki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Disgusted that he would try and place hands\Non Hanuki-san while he was still with Kaori-san,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew I had no choice but\Nto win this drinking battle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somehow, I was victorious! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then I was met with yet\Nanother unexpected turn of events.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our once in a lifetime chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... Kaori's the only one for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body shakes thinking this might\Nbe the last time I hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am loved once more by Jougasaki,\Na different me will surely sprout.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The me who is here now\Nonly exists in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me with you and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- "We're eloping. Thank you for everything.\N- Kaori," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Jougasaki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0} is getting wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm glad. I've never\Ngotten wet from the rain before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, student...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Student, what might you wish to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't asked you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You are dissatisfied, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I had no idea what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, opportunity is\Nalways dangling in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:18:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please grab onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 7,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the rain lets up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll head to Kyoto Station and buy\Ntrain tickets to as far away as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll head to a\Ncountry at the end of the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and live near a small town in a small house...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working in a strange land will surely be tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but seeing your smile when\NI come home will give me cheer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before long, we'll have a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your parents who were against\Nthis will surely come to accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The days and months pass by,\Nand at length we have grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I realize I have lived only for\Nthat day, tears fall from my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the happiest days of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But suddenly you fall ill, and\NI grasp your hand, nursing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiling, you say "I'm so glad I met you."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no, that's what I should be saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we promise that I'd be the first to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so glad we were able to be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this isn't an opportunity, then what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, this here's a\N100% full-blown opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her face, she's waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0} isn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how high-class her face looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inside her heart is the same\Nburning passion that's inside yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think she came with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? She's been looking at you the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we part, I want to share your warmth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you let me feel like I am loved?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that to you this\Nisn't a passionate, burning love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now the warmth of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the one thing that can\Nmake me feel like I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't? Is it because I'm not a real person?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a doll without a heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:19:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, you coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to spend the rest of\Nyour life a pitiful late-bloomer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with being called a "safe bet"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about her shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she wants you to thrust\Nyour burning passion upon her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been waiting this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am, after all, a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then make her a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you come and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it... I'll do it for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}! Johnny, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sick bastard!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is how it should be. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had almost lost my pure heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would never have been able to\Nlove Kaori-san in a pure manner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is a path unable to be\Ntread by we normal people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jougasaki and Kaori-san,\Nkeep going down that path together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if Keiko-san waited\Nfor me at the place she said?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps she was the most preferable choice?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to return to that scene once again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Retake! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to meet Keiko-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
